**Stage 1.** We obtain a plug-in estimate \(\) of the nuisance parameters \(=(,_{0},_{1})\). Note that since we assume that the propensity score is known, we only need to estimate \(_{0}\) and \(_{1}\) using \(_{0}\) and \(_{1}\).

